Program: Start the Week
Title: Gavin Turk on the Value of Art
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/b01s46g5
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 29 Apr 2013
On Start the Week Lisa Jardine talks to the artist Gavin Turk about the construction of artistic myth and the question of authorship and authenticity. The rare book dealer Rick Gekoski searches for lost treasures amid tales of theft, forgery and destruction, while the curator Paul Roberts reveals the life and culture preserved in the volcanic devastation of Pompeii and Herculaneum. The everyday object - a table - is at the centre of Tanya Ronder's new play of belonging, identity and inheritance. Producer: Katy Hickman. Show less